Package: ggGam
Type: Package
Title: Make prediction and diagnostic plots of an object of class `gam` generated by the gam function of the `mgcv` package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Keon-Woong Moon
Maintainer: Keon-Woong Moon <cardiomoon@gmail.com>
Description: You can make prediction plots of an object of class `gam` generated by the gam function of the `mgcv` package. 
         You can make diagnostic plots and Kaplan-Meier survival plot from a survival model.
Depends: R (>= 2.14.0)
Imports: ggplot2(>= 3.3.0),
         mgcv (>= 1.8-31),
         dplyr,
         tidyr,
         tidyselect,
         predict3d,
         ggpubr
Suggests: ISLR,
          gamair,
          survival
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
